নের) মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_070_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59661,"position":7,"arabic":"ضَيْقٍۢ","translation":"সংকীর্ণ","audioUrl":"wbw/027_070_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59662,"position":8,"arabic":"مِّمَّا","translation":"তা হ'তে যা","audioUrl":"wbw/027_070_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59663,"position":9,"arabic":"يَمْكُرُونَ","translation":"তারা ষড়যন্ত্র করছে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_070_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59664,"position":10,"arabic":"٧٠","translation":"(৭০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":71,"arabic":"وَيَقُولُونَ مَتَىٰ هَٰذَا ٱلْوَعْدُ إِن كُنتُمْ صَٰدِقِينَ","translation":"And [when] they ask, “When is this promise [of resurrection] to be fulfilled? [Answer this, O you who believe in it,] if you are men of truth!” –","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3230.mp3","surahId":27,"words":[{"id":60209,"position":1,"arabic":"وَيَقُولُونَ","translation":"এবং তারা বলে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_071_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60210,"position":2,"arabic":"مَتَىٰ","translation":"\"কখন","audioUrl":"wbw/027_071_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60211,"position":3,"arabic":"هَـٰذَا","translation":"এই","audioUrl":"wbw/027_071_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60212,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْوَعْدُ","translation":"প্রতিশ্রুতি (কার্যকর হবে)","audioUrl":"wbw/027_071_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60213,"position":5,"arabic":"إِن","translation":"যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/027_071_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60214,"position":6,"arabic":"كُنتُمْ","translation":"হও তোমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/027_071_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60215,"position":7,"arabic":"صَـٰدِقِينَ","translation":"সত্যবাদী\"","audioUrl":"wbw/027_071_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60216,"position":8,"arabic":"٧١","translation":"(৭১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":72,"arabic":"قُلْ عَسَىٰٓ أَن يَكُونَ رَدِفَ لَكُم بَعْضُ ٱلَّذِى تَسْتَعْجِلُونَ","translation":"say thou: “It may well be that something of that which [in your ignorance] you so hastily demands has already drawn close unto you.”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3231.mp3","surahId":27,"words":[{"id":60751,"position":1,"arabic":"قُلْ","translation":"বলো","audioUrl":"wbw/027_072_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60752,"position":2,"arabic":"عَسَىٰٓ","translation":"\"সম্ভবতঃ","audioUrl":"wbw/027_072_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60753,"position":3,"arabic":"أَن","translation":"(এমন) যে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_072_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60754,"position":4,"arabic":"يَكُونَ","translation":"তা হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/027_072_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60755,"position":5,"arabic":"رَدِفَ","translation":"নিকটবর্তী হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_072_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60756,"position":6,"arabic":"لَكُم","translation":"জন্যে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/027_072_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60757,"position":7,"arabic":"بَعْضُ","translation":"(তার) কিছুটা","audioUrl":"wbw/027_072_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60758,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/027_072_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60759,"position":9,"arabic":"تَسْتَعْجِلُونَ","translation":"তোমরা তাড়াতাড়ি করতে চাও\"","audioUrl":"wbw/027_072_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60760,"position":10,"arabic":"٧٢","translation":"(৭২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":73,"arabic":"وَإِنَّ رَبَّكَ لَذُو فَضْلٍ عَلَى ٱلنَّاسِ وَلَٰكِنَّ أَكْثَرَهُمْ لَا يَشْكُرُونَ","translation":"Now, verily, thy Sustainer is indeed limitless in His bounty unto men - but most of them are bereft of gratitude.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3232.mp3","surahId":27,"words":[{"id":61233,"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِنَّ","translation":"এবং নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/027_073_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61234,"position":2,"arabic":"رَبَّكَ","translation":"তোমার